title: Instructions
content: In this study, we'd like you to make judgments about how likely it is that someone would do something. First we'll tell you about the situation.

title: Background information
content: Justin recently realized that he needs $1000 in a few days, but he doesn't have it yet.

title: Your job in this study will be to answer this question: How likely is that Justin would actually do each thing?
content: Go to the next page to start seeing different proposals for what Justin could do.
